Linking to a UIM Page
The URI of Cúram application pages includes the locale code as the first part of the resource path,
for example, en/Person_homePage.do. This path is relative to the application's context
root, which corresponds to the WebContent folder in the development environment.
Therefore, all UIM pages are considered to be in a locale “folder”. When one UIM page is linked
to another, it is always in the same locale (or “folder”). Therefore, the locale is not specified
in the URI when a link is generated. For example, in the sample code that is shown here, the
